"{\"uid\": \"connexionfrance.com-news-what-is-now-known-about-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-on-friday-670153\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe to The Connexion  See prices & plans  HELP GUIDES  Income Tax in France  Healthcare in France  Inheritance Law and Wills in France  Visas and residency cards for France  Subscribe to The Connexion  See prices & plans  HELP GUIDES  Income Tax in France  Healthcare in France  Inheritance Law and Wills in France  Visas and residency cards for France        The 2024 Paris Olympic Games launch this week after years of preparation.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first event will be a Rugby Sevens match on Wednesday (July 24) but most people will see the opening ceremony as the traditional curtain raiser.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.089979028934768e-13, \"text\": \"Rugby Sevens\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony will be held on Friday (July 26), and although some plans are still being kept secret, other details about the event have now been made available.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been widely publicised that for the first time in the Summer Games' modern history, the opening ceremony will not be held inside a stadium, but rather outside.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will travel in boats along the river Seine, between the Austerlitz and I\\u00e9na bridges, passing some of the city's most famous sites.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"score\": 0.7286538962924114, \"rank\": 0.3723936770094429, \"text\": \"Austerlitz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each boat will take around 45 minutes to make the journey between the bridges.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They will travel as a convoy.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will culminate with a spectacle at the Trocad\\u00e9ro, opposite the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"score\": 0.9730907954876998, \"rank\": 0.023351147168026228, \"text\": \"Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Much of the riverbank has already been closed off, accessed only via QR codes for residents and workers, and temporary seating has been installed along the show's path.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Olympic QR codes begin: what Paris residents and visitors need to know  Rather creatively, the ceremony will officially start at 20:24 Paris time, and last for around three hours and 45 minutes.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3378202791106234e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3378202791106234e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exact details are being kept under wraps but hints from producer of the show Thomas Jolly suggest the iconic landmarks the athletes' boats pass by will tie into the ceremony, promoting the history and culture not just of Paris but of France.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3378202791106234e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whilst there were originally plans for the opening ceremony to be more widely accessible (up to 600,000 attendees), security concerns mean the event is now ticket-only with 300,000 tickets being available.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some tickets were handed out for free, with the remainder being available to purchase.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This close to the ceremony, however, only the most expensive tickets are available.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The officialOlympic websiteis still selling tickets for the show with the cheapest starting at \\u20ac900 per person, rising to \\u20ac2,700.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony will be shown across TV channels throughout the world, including France 2 in France, NBC in the US, and the BBC in the UK.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999576720456398, \"rank\": 2.464671861230896e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997629478445649, \"rank\": 0.00023710836178895479, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remaining tickets for events are also on sale through the Olympic website.\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The good news is that early forecasts are for a 'typical' Parisian summer evening.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Temperatures in the day will be close to 30C but will begin to drop by the start of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skies are likely to remain clear although rain forecast in the neighbouring regions of Normandy and Hauts-de-France could mean some clouds will reach the city.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"score\": 0.9999767552649677, \"rank\": 2.3237216183566482e-05, \"text\": \"Normandy\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\"}, {\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hauts-de-France\", \"score\": 0.9998931542795289, \"rank\": 0.00010685713773947294, \"text\": \"Hauts-de-France\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hauts-de-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hauts-de-France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One concern is the power of the Seine - the river's currents are currently stronger than usual for summer, meaning boats may need to drive slower to prevent athletes being thrown around.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2975, \"end\": 2980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2489802132195888e-19, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a ceremony planned so meticulously, this may have some knock-on effects in regards to timing.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Weather in France July 22 - July 26: Forecast by area this week  Security for the event is, as expected, massive, with some 45,000 police officers and security personnel being deployed along the route.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0872051246047761e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snipers and anti-terrorist specialists will also be camped out on buildings looking for potential danger and anti-drone squads will be set up beside the capital.\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If fear of an attack is deemed too high nearer the time, there are alternative plans, which would see the opening ceremony held either at the Trocad\\u00e9ro alone, or in the Stade de France in nearby Seine-Saint-Denis, come into play.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"score\": 0.9730907954876998, \"rank\": 0.023351147168026228, \"text\": \"Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Drones, divers, dogs: the massive job of making Paris Olympics secure  Up to three million distributed sensors provide dangerously low readings  Warm spell comes despite rain in west and north  Father Christmas may be known for his present delivery on December 24, but in the east of France, another bearded figure bearing gifts is celebrated much earlier in the month  Wealthy households must make advance payment before final amounts calculated via spring tax return  Local residents rally to help two well-known traders    A reader writes of his experiences with the company  Station in Brittany will include six ultra-fast charging points  When to buy depends if you want a Nordmann fir, a Norway spruce, or an alternative  Homeowners now have until 2030 to set up the devices  Up to three million distributed sensors provide dangerously low readings  Father Christmas may be known for his present delivery on December 24, but in the east of France, another bearded figure bearing gifts is celebrated much earlier in the month  A useful saying for the festive season when hot cider is served in markets  James Campbell reinvents classic p\\u00e2tisserie creations with a contemporary Japanese twist, all made achievable to the home cook  Jo MacDonald, 59, describes how she monetised her hobby in Gers    Both household electricity and gas bills will increase  Issue now drawing attention at the highest levels  Second-home owners must pay their taxe d'habitation this month  Warm spell comes despite rain in west and north  Vote reverses proposal to lower tax exemption thresholds for self-employed workers    Customers can take home a piece of the capital's 